{
  "stem": "4764.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was some sort of escape mechanism, where there was a-- people used to meet other-- you know, other people used to meet other people sort of thing, right?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we actually came to this town, which was the first city I had ever seen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was Bratislava, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were supposed to go by train there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Someone else picked us up there and took us to a sort of fairly modern-looking building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was-- it was very bad, because the sink in the bathroom, the porcelain was broken.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother cut her hand on it while trying to wash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also, I had to clean my shoes that night, because I had been walking  in these shoes, and we were supposed to go on the train and look like we were citizens of the world.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we looked-- I suppose we must've looked very bedraggled, and everybody spent the night sprucing themselves up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my mother said to me, you've got to clean your shoes so that they look very clean, because the next morning you are-- we were going on a train, and you had-- you weren't supposed to look like you'd just walked over the mountains.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You were supposed to look like citizens of the-- of the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and-- and for-- I mean, we-- I didn't mention we had foreign papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Our names were changed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my mother said, if somebody asks you, your name is [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Mattera, ?] not Muller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Stephan [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Mattera. ?] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that night we had to clean all our clothes and our shoes so that we would look reasonable the next day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And your mother cut her hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She cut her hand on the sink.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
